window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Christmas elves: Everything you thought you knew is wrong.</p> <p>Newly appointed Christmas Special Investigator Steingrim Og's first day on the job is interrupted by a murder and theft of a magic item, which threatens to destroy all society at the North Pole. With no mentor, on-the-job training is all Steingrim has to rely on.</p> <p>Fighting racism, corruption, and politics, Steingrim finds his first case more complex than he imagined. He only has five days to find the murderer and the missing magic item, or everything the Elves know will come undone.</p>"; 
